	<body>
		<outline text="Video cameras, computer mice, and the 2000s in general are my usual topics. I&#39;m sure I&#39;ll waver eventually.&#xA;&#xA;I hate capitalism and I&#39;m not here to get sponsorships, I just want to share what I&#39;m up to for your entertainment and education.&#xA;&#xA;On my side channel (below) I sometimes upload smaller clips, and I do streams on some weekends.&#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/CathodeRayDude.xml" title="Cathode Ray Dude - CRD"></outline>
		<outline text="Gigguk here. I&#39;m actually gonna try and use this second channel.&#xA;&#xA;FOR MY MAIN CHANNEL GO HERE:&#xA;http://www.youtube.com/gigguk&#xA;&#xA;Did I mention I have a twitter?&#xA;http://twitter.com/#!/GiggukAZ" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/Garnt.xml" title="Garnt"></outline>
		<outline text="An element of truth - videos about science, education, and anything else I find interesting." type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/Veritasium.xml" title="Veritasium"></outline>
		<outline text="TeClas é um canal sobre tecnologia e luta de classes, digitado pelos camaradas @ayanicodemos @azhariel.tv @eai_pequi @lsaporiti @tresgatosnumjaleco e @lfzawacki ✊" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/TeClas.xml" title="Tecnologia e Classe (TeClas)"></outline>
		<outline text="Meu nome é Guilherme, mas aqui e na internet em geral me chamam de Funky.&#xA;Eu comecei meu canal em 2011 jogando e comentando partidas de Call of Duty, mas logo meu conteúdo abrangeu games em geral. O foco aqui é em séries de let&#39;s plays, mas de vez em quando rola algo diferente e até vlogs de assuntos aleatórios.&#xA;&#xA;&#34;Funky Black Cat&#34; era minha gamertag na Xbox Live antes de abrir o canal, que começou com o nome &#34;Comentando COD&#34;.&#xA;Obviamente esse nome era terrível, então eu decidi renomeá-lo pra minha gamertag ainda no começo do canal.&#xA;&#xA;O nome &#34;Funky&#34; vem da música &#34;Funky Monks&#34; do Red Hot Chili Peppers, e também do estilo musical da banda.&#xA;&#34;Black Cat&#34; completa o nome pra soar parecido com &#34;Jumping Jack Flash&#34;, música dos Rolling Stones. O gato preto de quebra acabou se tornando mascote do canal.&#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/Funky.xml" title="Funky Black Cat"></outline>
		<outline text="Saving Caribbean Culture with Commentary&#xA;Business Inquiries: foreignmaninaforeignland@nebula.tv" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/ForeignManForeignLand.xml" title="Foreign Man in a Foreign Land"></outline>
		<outline text="Hello. I make videos primarily to share thoughts about various topics I find interesting. So far, they&#39;ve mostly been about language learning, but I have many videos planned about other topics as well, such as art, programming, games, and so on!" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/Livlaki.xml" title="Livakivi"></outline>
		<outline text="Want to subconsciously learn while being entertained? Then subscribe!!  &#xA;My twitter: https://twitter.com/ElectroBOOMGuy&#xA;My Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mehdi_sadaghdar&#xA;My Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/ElectroBOOM&#xA;My videos are also available on Odysee in the link below, in case YouTube decides to remove them. Subscribe there too:&#xA;https://odysee.com/$/invite/@ElectroBOOM:9&#xA;&#xA;If you like my content and like to support your favorite creator, you can visit my page here: http://www.patreon.com/electroboom&#xA;Check my Merch and T-Shirts at: https://teespring.com/stores/electroboom&#xA;&#xA;And I have some articles in my website: http://electroboom.com&#xA;&#xA;See my awesome and generous sponsors here: https://www.electroboom.com/?page_id=727 &#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/ElectroBoom.xml" title="ElectroBOOM"></outline>
		<outline text="Welcome to Usagi Electric!&#xA;&#xA;On this channel, we dive into old school technology, focusing heavily on vacuum tubes. My primary goal is to build computing circuits based off the legendary machines of yesteryear, only with a slight modern twist. All the tubes will be operating with very low voltages on the plate, making the projects safe and easy to follow along with. So, lets grab our multimeters, some random tubes and a low voltage power supply and have fun!&#xA;&#xA;Usagi Electric covers one of my main passions, while my other main passion can be found over on Usagi Motors." type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/UsagiElectric.xml" title="Usagi Electric"></outline>
		<outline text="For all general enquiries feel free to contact me through any social media service listed below,&#xA;If you&#39;d like to longer form something longer form like fan mail or you have a video suggestion, feel free to send me an email.&#xA;&#xA;If you&#39;d like to chat, then come join my Discord: https://brodierobertson.xyz/discord&#xA;All of the scripts and configs that I write are available on my GitHub.&#xA;Email: brodierobertsonbusiness@gmail.com&#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/BrodieRobertson.xml" title="Brodie Robertson"></outline>
		<outline text="Learn about the history and folklore of Japan! Occasionally funny.&#xA;&#xA;MERCH: https://shop.linfamy.com/&#xA;(charms, stickers, tees, and more!)&#xA;&#xA;Send me mail:&#xA;1090 S Milpitas Blvd #263&#xA;Milpitas, CA 95035&#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/Linfamy.xml" title="Linfamy"></outline>
