		<outline text="Signified B Sides is basically my rant space for content and topics that don&#39;t really fit into the main channel.  Videos here will be even more unpolished and less scripted. I plan on doing addendums to the main videos as well as rants on topics that don&#39;t fully fit into the scope of the main channel. Ideally, eventually, I&#39;ll maybe have some commentary tracks and things like that.  " type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/SignifierBSides.xml" title="Signified B Sides"></outline>
