		<outline text="I make videos about things I like.&#xA;&#xA;My Twitter is @eyepatchwolf: https://twitter.com/EyePatchWolf&#xA;&#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/EyePatchWolf.xml" title="Super Eyepatch Wolf"></outline>
		<outline text="📼Just some guy📼&#xA;I discuss lost media, anime to watch, &amp; some of the worst anime of all time.  Whatever you&#39;re here for, you can be sure kenny lauderdale has you covered. This channel is about covering japanese shows on Laserdisc, lost anime, &amp; cursed VHS tapes most people have never even heard of. If that sounds good to you then you&#39;re in the right place.&#xA;https://x.com/KennyLauderdal3&#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/KennyLaudelaire.xml" title="kenny lauderdale"></outline>
		<outline text="Welcome, I&#39;m Josh Strife Hayes, I critique and analyse videogames.&#xA;&#xA;This channel is all about playing those games we all love and asking, were they really that good?&#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/JoshStrifePlays.xml" title="Josh Strife Plays"></outline>
		<outline text="My name is Stevem, not STEVE, M. Stevemmmm as in Steven with an &#34;m&#39;.&#xA;I make Video Essays about Animation History that focus on the old, obscure and Japanese. Sometimes I make videos about Japanese music.&#xA;https://stevem.gimmeswag.com&#xA;" type="rss" xmlUrl="https://feed.rodhfr.shop/STEVEM.xml" title="STEVEM"></outline>
